nt-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">4. 지급기간 : 2026년~2027년 (최대 2년) * 단, 4학년의 경우 1년간 지급</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">5. </span>자격요건</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">가<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">현재 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">3</span>학년 또는 4학년 재학 중인 이공계열 전공자(의치약학 계열 제외)</u></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">나<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. 전체 </span>이수학기 총 평균평점이 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">3.0 </span>이상인자</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">소득분위 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">5</span>분위 이하인 자</u></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">라<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. <u>타 기관(기업, 단체 등)으로부터 별도의 생활비성 장학금을 지원 받지 않는 자</u></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">6. </span>제출서류</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">가<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>장학금 지원신청서<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>양식<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">) 1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">나<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. 지도교수,학과장,학장 등 추천서(양식) 1부</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>서약서<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>양식<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">) 1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">라<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>가족관계증명서 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">마<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>증명사진<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>최근 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">3</span>개월이내에 촬영한 사진을 장학금 지원신청서에 부착할 것)</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">바<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>신청자 이력사항<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>양식<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">) 1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">사<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>자기소개 및 학업계획서<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>양식<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">) 1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">아<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>성적증명서 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">자<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>개인정보 수집이용 동의서(양식) <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">차<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>소득분위 확인서<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>한국장학재단 발급<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">카. 건강보험료 납부확인서 1부</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">타. 본인 명의 통장사본</span> <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span>부</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> </span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">7. 일정</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">가. 신청 기간 : <strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">~2026.04.24(금) 16시까지</u></span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">나. 장학생 최종자 선정(재단) : 2026.05.08(금) 예정</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">다. 상반기 장학금 지급 일정 : 2026.05.29(금) 예정</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'> </p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">8. </span>유의사항</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">가<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>추후 지원서의 허위작성 및 누락<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>작성 상 하자가 있을 경우 불합격 처리됨</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">나<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>작성내용은 증빙서류 제출 시에만 인정되면<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">, </span>증빙서류는 신청일 기준 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">1</span>개월 이내 발급분부터 유효함</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">다<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>선발된 장학생에 대한 장학금 지급은 선발 후 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">2</span>년간 연속 수혜를 원칙으로 함</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">라<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">. </span>휴학 및 학적 변동 시<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">(</span>군입대, 휴학, 취업, 편입, 졸업 등<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">) </span>지급 대상에서 제외 됨</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\">마. 장학생은 장학증서 수여식을 비롯한 재단에서 실시하는 행사에 적극적으로 참여해야 함</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> </span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">9. </span><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"><u><strong>제출처 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">:</span></strong></u></span></span></span><u><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"> 장학팀 대표메일</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\"><a href=\"mailto:student@dongguk.edu\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\"> (student@dongguk.edu</span></a><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\">) “</span></span><span style=\"color:#0000FF;\">인탑스평산장학 신청_홍길동<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">”</span>으로 제목 쓸 것</span></span></span></strong></u></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> </span></span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"0\" style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Pretendard, 나눔고딕, NanumGothic, \"Nanum Gothic\", 돋움, Dotum, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.2;'><span style=\"font-family:굴림;\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">* </span>문의 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">: </span>장학팀 장학담당 <span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; letter-spacing: 0pt;\">02)2260-3698,3043</span></span></span></span></span></p>",
    "본문": "<2026학년도 인탑스평산장학재단 장학생 선발 안내>\n1.\n재단명\n:\n인탑스평산장학재단\n2.\n추천인원\n: 2\n명\n※\n학교추천 후 재단심사를 통해 최종 선발\n3.\n지원금액\n:\n연\n6\n백만원\n(1\n인당\n) (연 2회 분할 지급, 각 300만원, 생활비성 장학)\n4. 지급기간 : 2026년~2027년 (최대 2년) * 단, 4학년의 경우 1년간 지급\n5.\n자격요건\n가\n.\n현재\n3\n학년 또는 4학년 재학 중인 이공계열 전공자(의치약학 계열 제외)\n나\n. 전체\n이수학기 총 평균평점이\n3.0\n이상인자\n다\n.\n소득분위\n5\n분위 이하인 자\n라\n.\n타 기관(기업, 단체 등)으로부터 별도의 생활비성 장학금을 지원 받지 않는 자\n6.\n제출서류\n가\n.\n장학금 지원신청서\n(\n양식\n) 1\n부\n나\n. 지도교수,학과장,학장 등 추천서(양식) 1부\n다\n.\n서약서\n(\n양식\n) 1\n부\n라\n.\n가족관계증명서\n1\n부\n마\n.\n증명사진\n(\n최근\n3\n개월이내에 촬영한 사진을 장학금 지원신청서에 부착할 것)\n바\n.\n신청자 이력사항\n(\n양식\n) 1\n부\n사\n.\n자기소개 및 학업계획서\n(\n양식\n) 1\n부\n아\n.\n성적증명서\n1\n부\n자\n.\n개인정보 수집이용 동의서(양식)\n1\n부\n차\n.\n소득분위 확인서\n(\n한국장학재단 발급\n)\n카. 건강보험료 납부확인서 1부\n타. 본인 명의 통장사본\n1\n부\n7. 일정\n가. 신청 기간 :\n~2026.04.24(금) 16시까지\n나. 장학생 최종자 선정(재단) : 2026.05.08(금) 예정\n다. 상반기 장학금 지급 일정 : 2026.05.29(금) 예정\n8.\n유의사항\n가\n.\n추후 지원서의 허위작성 및 누락\n,\n작성 상 하자가 있을 경우 불합격 처리됨\n나\n.\n작성내용은 증빙서류 제출 시에만 인정되면\n,\n증빙서류는 신청일 기준\n1\n개월 이내 발급분부터 유효함\n다\n.\n선발된 장학생에 대한 장학금 지급은 선발 후\n2\n년간 연속 수혜를 원칙으로 함\n라\n.\n휴학 및 학적 변동 시\n(\n군입대, 휴학, 취업, 편입, 졸업 등\n)\n지급 대상에서 제외 됨\n마. 장학생은 장학증서 수여식을 비롯한 재단에서 실시하는 행사에 적극적으로 참여해야 함\n9.\n제출처\n:\n장학팀 대표메일\n(student@dongguk.edu\n) “\n인탑스평산장학 신청_홍길동\n”\n으로 제목 쓸 것\n*\n문의\n:\n장학팀 장학담당\n02)2260-3698,3043",
